1. *Takvom* neodgovornom ponašanju ne možemo tolerisati. (We cannot tolerate *such* irresponsible behavior.)
2. Odgovorio sam mu *takvim* tonom jer je to zaslužio. (I responded to him with *such* a tone because he deserved it.)
3. *Takvih* problema nismo imali ranije. (We didn't have *such* problems before.)
4. Moramo naći rešenje za *takvu* situaciju. (We need to find a solution for *such* a situation.)
5. Nisam videla *takve* prizore još od detinjstva. (I haven't seen *such* scenes since I was a child.)
6. *Takvo* ponašanje nije prihvatljivo u društvu. ( *Such* behavior is not acceptable in society.)
7. U ovom gradu ima *takvih* lepih mesta. (There are *such* beautiful places in this city.)
8. *Takvim* argumentima ne može se osporiti činjenica. (The fact cannot be disputed with *such* arguments.)
9. Ne mogu da verujem da postoji *takva* situacija. (I can't believe there is *such* a situation.)
10. *Takve* vesti uznemirile su me. (I was upset by *such* news.)